<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>✨<sp/>What<sp/>is<sp/>LARS?</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">**LARS**<sp/>(Light<sp/>Augmented<sp/>Reality<sp/>System)<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>cross-platform,<sp/>open-source<sp/>framework<sp/>for<sp/>*experimentation,<sp/>education,<sp/>and<sp/>outreach*<sp/>in<sp/>collective<sp/>robotics.<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">It<sp/>leverages<sp/>Extended<sp/>Reality<sp/>(XR)<sp/>to<sp/>seamlessly<sp/>merge<sp/>the<sp/>physical<sp/>and<sp/>virtual<sp/>worlds,<sp/>projecting<sp/>dynamic<sp/>visual<sp/>objects—such<sp/>as<sp/>gradients,<sp/>fields,<sp/>trails,<sp/>and<sp/>even<sp/>robot<sp/>states—directly<sp/>into<sp/>the<sp/>environment<sp/>where<sp/>real<sp/>robots<sp/>operate.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">LARS<sp/>enables<sp/>**indirect<sp/>robot-robot<sp/>communication**<sp/>(stigmergy),<sp/>while<sp/>preserving<sp/>all<sp/>real-world<sp/>constraints.<sp/>It<sp/>turns<sp/>&quot;invisible&quot;<sp/>swarm<sp/>dynamics<sp/>into<sp/>tangible,<sp/>interactive<sp/>experiences<sp/>for<sp/>researchers,<sp/>students,<sp/>and<sp/>the<sp/>public.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">---</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
