<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Projection<sp/>of<sp/>Virtual,<sp/>Visual<sp/>Objects**<sp/>🔦<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Marker-Free,<sp/>Cross-platform<sp/>Detection<sp/>and<sp/>Tracking<sp/>System<sp/>(based<sp/>on<sp/>ARK)**<sp/>🎯<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Real-Time<sp/>Performance**<sp/>⚡<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Standalone<sp/>System**<sp/>🖥️<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Scalability<sp/>to<sp/>Collective<sp/>Size**<sp/>📈<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Indirect<sp/>Robot-Robot<sp/>(Stigmergy)<sp/>🐜<sp/>and<sp/>Human-Robot<sp/>Communication**<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Direct<sp/>Communication<sp/>Possibility**<sp/>📡<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**Ease<sp/>of<sp/>Setup<sp/>and<sp/>Robustness**<sp/>🛠️<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
