<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Promoting<sp/>science<sp/>communication<sp/>and<sp/>public<sp/>engagement<sp/>by<sp/>showcasing<sp/>embodied<sp/>collective<sp/>behaviors<sp/>of<sp/>robots</highlight></codeline>
