<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>🏗️<sp/>Architecture<sp/>Overview</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">LARS<sp/>is<sp/>built<sp/>on<sp/>the<sp/>classic<sp/>**Model-View-Controller<sp/>(MVC)**<sp/>pattern:</highlight></codeline>
