<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>🖼️<sp/>**View:**<sp/>GUI,<sp/>visualization,<sp/>and<sp/>projector<sp/>output<sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>🎮<sp/>**Controller:**<sp/>Experiment<sp/>orchestration,<sp/>tracking,<sp/>and<sp/>logic</highlight></codeline>
